https://engineering.berkeley.edu/student-services/register-classes says that

  • April 1:  Schedule of Classses available
  • April 1:  Phase I and Phase II appointment times available in CalCentral
  • April 15: Enrollment begins

PS, only newly admitted students have phase 1 during the summer :) perk of being a returning student. You can see this by googling "berkeley academic calendar" or "berkeley student enrollment calendar" for the exact dates
